	abstract = {Objective: To summarize how artiÔ¨Åcial intelligence (AI) is being applied in COVID-19 research and determine whether these AI applications integrated heterogenous data from different sources for modeling. Materials and Methods: We searched 2 major COVID-19 literature databases, the National Institutes of Health‚Äôs LitCovid and the World Health Organization‚Äôs COVID-19 database on March 9, 2021. Following the Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analyses (PRISMA) guideline, 2 reviewers independently reviewed all the articles in 2 rounds of screening.
